ink-morrissey-liked-me-3831556">史密斯乐队处女作的后期制作人约翰·波特：“我不认为莫里西喜欢我”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Smiths-L-R-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-Morrissey-and-Johnny-Marr-perform-live-on-stage-1984.-CREDIT_-Pete-Cronin_Redferns_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯乐队</a>首张同名专辑的制作人约翰·波特透露，他认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morrissey">莫里西</a>不喜欢他。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-smiths-every-song-ranked-in-order-of-greatness-3589477">史密斯乐队：每首歌都按伟大程度排列</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.musicradar.com/artists/i-dont-think-morrissey-liked-me-i-dont-think-he-liked-my-friendship-with-johnny-producer-john-porter-on-shaping-the-smiths-most-iconic-tracks-and-why-hes-auctioning-a-treasure-trove-of-original-acetates?fbclid=IwY2xjawH_MFJleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHZ_jbsEYZGagQCJFGU3MoxURBf64FInaWb2KZFnAGR-0nLuE-KgNT1TLuQ_aem_zjJKklmTYOCI3JRvjOnzNQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐雷达</em></a>的新采访中，波特回顾了他在 1984 年这张具有开创性意义的专辑中的工作，以及他如何向乐队传授音乐制作知识。</p><p>波特解释说，虽然<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-marr">约翰尼·马尔</a>对他对这一过程的解释“立即感兴趣”，但莫里西的“目光呆滞”。</p><p> “我真的很喜欢与史密斯乐队一起工作，但莫里西总是很困难，”他补充道。 “当我第一次见到他时，他非常有礼貌，会给我寄明信片，说他非常喜欢它，并感谢我。这很快就变成了彻底的蔑视。我不认为莫里西喜欢我。我认为他不喜欢我和约翰尼的友谊。” </p><figure id="attachment_3792946" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792946" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792946" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270.jpg" alt="史密斯夫妇的约翰尼·马尔和莫里西" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/johnny-marr-morrissey-the-smiths@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792946" class="wp-caption-text">史密斯乐队的约翰尼·马尔和莫里西。图片来源：克莱尔·穆勒/雷德芬斯</figcaption></figure><p>这位制作人后来与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-adams">瑞安·亚当斯 (Ryan Adams)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-costello">埃尔维斯·科斯特洛 (Elvis Costello)</a>和卡洛斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carlos-santana">桑塔纳</a>(Carlos Santana) 等人合作过，他接着详细介绍了史密斯乐队 (The Smiths) 厂牌 Rough Trade Records 的创始人杰夫·特拉维斯 (Geoff Travis) 在不认可他在这首歌中的工作后最终解雇了他。现在多久了”。</p><p> “杰夫的观点是我玩得太开心了，而且听起来不像史密斯一家，”他解释道。 “杰夫解雇我后，约翰尼希望我继续做事。所以我回来和他们一起做了几首单曲，但后来他们开始全职与史蒂芬[斯特里特]合作。</p><p> “从某种意义上说，这对我来说很令人沮丧。我的意思是，你知道，你与乐队建立了关系。我想我们才刚刚开始真正取得进展。”</p><p>波特目前正在拍卖自 20 世纪 80 年代以来从未播放过的多首原始测试压片、醋酸盐和原始混音。投标将于明天（1 月 24 日）下午 2 点（格林威治标准时间<a href="https://www.easyliveauction.com/catalogue/d9bf474fc36ec3394604ca300c1e9d70/0af8d24542e81eb9357e7ef448a6646f/vinyl-records-the-john-porter-collection-of-acetates-mast/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">）</a>开始。 </p><figure id="attachment_3445544" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3445544" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3445544" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute.jpg" alt="史密斯乐队的约翰尼·马尔、莫里西、迈克·乔伊斯和安迪·洛克于 1985 年合影" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TheSmiths-Andy-Rourke-Mike-Joyce-tribute-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3445544" class="wp-caption-text"> 1985 年，史密斯乐队的约翰尼·马尔、莫里西、迈克·乔伊斯和安迪·洛克。图片来源：Getty</figcaption></figure><p>去年，在史密斯乐队的其他新闻中，莫里西解释了为什么<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-on-why-he-wanted-the-smiths-reunion-tour-it-wasnt-because-i-had-any-emotional-attachment-to-johnny-marr-i-have-absolutely-none-3821217">他希望乐队重聚进行现场巡演，</a>声称这与他对前乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-marr">约翰尼·马尔</a>的“任何情感依恋”无关，尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-opens-up-about-recent-morrissey-spat-you-have-to-defend-yourself-3170304">两人之间一直存在不和。</a> 。</p><p>今年夏天，这位前主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-hits-out-at-johnny-marr-for-turning-down-lucrative-the-smiths-reunion-which-he-agreed-to-3788683">表示他已同意参加 2025 年史密斯乐队的“利润丰厚”巡演，但声称马尔“忽略”了这一提议</a>。</p><p>后来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-responds-to-morrisseys-claims-he-ignored-a-reunion-tour-offer-i-didnt-ignore-the-offer-i-said-no-3794610">这位吉他手管理团队的一名代表在 X/Twitter 上的一份声明中称莫里西的评论“不正确”</a> ，马尔在自己的消息中补充道：“我没有忽视这个提议——我说了不”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/producer-of-the-smiths-debut-john-porter-i-dont-think-morrissey-liked-me-3831556">史密斯乐队处女作的后期制作人约翰·波特：“我不认为莫里西喜欢我”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
