以下是 2025 年全英音乐奖的所有提名者https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=brit-awards-2025-nomineesLiberty Dunworth Thu, 23 Jan 2025 17:30:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeBRIT AwardsGrimeHip-hopIndieMetalPopR&BRapRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3831514 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="RAYE 出席 2024 年全英音乐奖" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Charli XCX、Dua Lipa、The Last Evening Party、Ezra Collective、Myles Smith 和 The Cure 都在下个月的颁奖典礼前获得了认可</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">《这是 2025 年全英音乐奖的所有提名者》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="RAYE 出席 2024 年全英音乐奖" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RAYE-BRITS@2000X1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025 年全英音乐奖</a>完整提名名单已公布。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-winners-nominations-list-3595742"><b>以下是 2024 年全英音乐奖的所有获奖者</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的颁奖典礼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/date-revealed-for-the-brit-awards-2025-3794739">将于 3 月 1 日星期六在伦敦 O2 举行</a>，并在 ITV1 和 ITVX 上独家播出。喜剧演员兼演员 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-jack-whitehall-to-return-as-host-3829454">杰克·怀特豪尔 (Jack Whitehall) 已被宣布担任回归主持人</a>，这是他继 2018 年、2019 年、2020 年和 2021 年之后第五次主持该颁奖典礼。</p><p>今年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>凭借最多的提名遥遥领先，获得了年度艺术家、流行表演和舞蹈表演等五个类别的提名。她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>合作的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">Guess》</a>也入围了年度歌曲奖，而她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">《BRAT》</a>唱片（为<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">BRAT Summer</a>提供了灵感）也入围了万事达卡年度专辑奖。</p><p>紧随其后的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">《Dua Lipa》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">《Ezra Collective》</a> ，它们分别获得了四项大奖。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/myles-smith">迈尔斯·史密斯 (Myles Smith)</a>已获得三个类别的提名，尽管他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-name-2025-rising-star-winner-3819335">之前被宣布为 2025 年新星奖的获得者</a>，这意味着他有可能在当晚带着四座奖杯离开。</p><p>另一个值得注意的成员是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">The Cure</a> ，他们凭借广受好评的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">“Songs Of A Lost World”</a>获得了三十多年来的首次全英提名，这是他们自 2008 年以来期待已久的第一张唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-smith">。</a> 。有机会赢得年度专辑、年度最佳组合和另类/摇滚表演类别。 </p><figure id="attachment_3810524" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3810524" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3810524" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024.jpg" alt="罗伯特·史密斯（丹尼尔·博查斯基/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robert-Smith-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3810524" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·史密斯（丹尼尔·博查斯基/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>还凭借其“最后”曲目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">“Now And Then”</a>入围万事达卡年度歌曲候选名单。这首单曲由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>创作，是最后一首包含所有成员的单曲，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-beatles-now-and-then-final-song-ai-documentary-peter-jackson-music-video-inside-story-3527104">使用人工智能技术恢复了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治·哈里森</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>之前的录音。</p><p>此次提名使其成为该乐队自 1977 年以来首次获得全英音乐奖提名，同年该奖项首次推出。</p><p>查看下面的完整提名者名单。</p><h2> <strong>2025 年全英音乐奖提名者为：</strong></h2><p><strong>万事达卡年度专辑<br /></strong>Charli XCX – “小子”<br /> The Cure——《失落世界之歌》<br /> Dua Lipa – “激进乐观主义”<br /> Ezra Collective – 《跳舞吧，没人在看》<br />最后的晚宴——“狂喜前奏”</p><p><strong>年度艺术家</strong><br />比巴杜比<br />中部中东欧<br />查理·XCX<br />杜阿·利帕<br />弗莱德又来了..<br />杰米xx<br />迈克尔·基瓦努卡<br />尼亚档案馆<br />雷切尔·奇努里里<br />萨姆·芬德</p><p><strong>年度最佳集团</strong><br />带给我的地平线<br />酷玩乐队<br />治愈方法<br />以斯拉集体<br />最后的晚宴</p><figure id="attachment_3793483" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793483" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793483" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Charli XCX 在 2024 年 H&amp;M&amp;LONDON 音乐活动上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793483" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年的 Charli XCX。图片来源：Samir Hussein/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p><strong>最佳新人奖</strong><br />英语老师<br />以斯拉集体<br />最后的晚宴<br />迈尔斯·史密斯<br />雷切尔·奇努里里</p><p><strong>万事达卡年度歌曲</strong><br />阿特玛斯 – “我喜欢你吻我的方式”<br />披头士乐队 – “现在和那时”<br /> Bl3ss 与 Camrin Watsin ft. bbyclose – &#39;Kisses&#39;<br /> Central Cee ft. Lil Baby –“BAND4BAND”<br /> Charli XCX ft. Billie Eilish – &#39;Guess&#39;<br /> Chase &amp; Status ft. Stormzy – &#39;Backbone&#39;<br />酷玩乐队 – &#39;feelslikeimfallinginlove&#39;<br />杜阿·利帕 – 《训练季》<br /> Ella Henderson ft. Rudimental – &#39;Alibi&#39;<br /> JADE——“我梦想中的天使”<br />乔丹·阿德通吉 – &#39;KEHLANI&#39;<br /> KSI ft. Trippie Redd – &#39;Thick Of It&#39;<br />迈尔斯·史密斯——《观星》<br />萨姆·莱德 – 《你对我来说就是圣诞节》<br />